Class AliasSwitch

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
CommandLineSwitch, Visitable
public class AliasSwitch
extends java.lang.Object
implements CommandLineSwitch

Passes its values to the switches it is an alias for. Use an alias switch to group many switches together and set them all at once with just one name.
